Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來 時宗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.29,0:00:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.19,0:00:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你是要將這機體送往哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭達斯境內 本公司的服務中心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是吉米·哈茲福特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯貝爾尼斯工業公司的技師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯貝爾尼斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼個製造商嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本公司是新銳企業
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,持有銀色殲滅者技術
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.60,0:00:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成為業界矚目的快速成長股
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.78,0:00:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是關注度持續升溫的企業
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.50,0:00:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那機體 是叫銀色{\rsymbol}…{\r}殲滅者{\rsymbol}…{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀色殲滅者{\rsymbol}…{\r}穩定型原型機
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最新銳的{\rsymbol}…{\r}U-link系統
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可將內載駕駛員的思維模式 轉入曳戰者的控制系統
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:01:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使性能上{\rsymbol}…{\r}有望獲得飛躍性提升
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此系統的採用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀色殲{\rsymbol}…{\r}殲滅者比以往的{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.57,0:01:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天黑之前儘量拉開距離
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.97,0:01:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶上那位小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.70,0:01:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.18,0:01:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.53,0:03:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1050,705)\fad(1000,1000))}覺醒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗 走路麻利點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當這路線變更是誰害的?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我害的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.07,0:03:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些反胃{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.03,0:03:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.95,0:03:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我吞回去堅持到下一個地點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他倆關係真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.29,0:03:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在只能向本該繞開的敵人腹地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不{\rsymbol}…{\r}不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.85,0:03:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少你不是軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是放心這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子 是運輸曳戰者途中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.93,0:04:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試圖將其截獲 結果反被幹掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻報告大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啟動流程
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.67,0:04:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次換個模式試試
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讀入識別編號的同時 清除存儲器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後動力部緊急啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 或許能行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動力部接入傳動系統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陀螺儀穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,固定支撐腳後向前邁步
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲 可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.70,0:04:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.88,0:05:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把時宗拽下來之後就一直這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全不聽使喚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.05,0:05:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,試過所有模式 全行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是第一次遇到戰爭知識不適用的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-link系統轉寫的是最初一名操縱者的思維模式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.66,0:05:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那男孩可以說已經成了啟動鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要講幾遍你們才懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍人是經驗主義
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,機師 進時宗上等兵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 他呀{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是初次上陣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次總難免如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.06,0:05:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位小姐不是說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.48,0:05:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓進時宗上等兵去駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.00,0:05:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人恐怕就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然成了鑰匙 就要盡到鑰匙的本分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可是戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是全部投降的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,投降者還會繼續增加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我軍必定會大舉反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 帶下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.89,0:06:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備做得怎樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.98,0:06:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受掃討作戰的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後續部隊抵達時間會稍有延誤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.10,0:06:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但能勉強趕上作戰時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.59,0:06:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳令務必趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.73,0:06:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進攻作戰的最終目標直搗敵人王都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果曳戰者不能有效展開 作戰會失去意義
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.44,0:06:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,報告一下那場莫名的戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是說有過格鬥戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並非槍械或刀劍之類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿蘭達斯的曳戰者應該沒有這類性能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.46,0:07:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實他們只有些過時的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新型嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,殘骸中 除一部阿蘭達斯機體外 全為我軍機體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但查不到所屬 很有可能是偽裝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:26.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士兵也查不到所屬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.44,0:07:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的偽裝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者說{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如何處理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那台新型曳戰者的去向讓人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼續追蹤調查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情報部的人可能與此有關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面我會想辦法應付
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.82,0:07:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掃討作戰中的部隊那邊 我這就去聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重點注意姿勢控制
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重心移動不要依靠腳跟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.23,0:08:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前進
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比之前還差了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按你說的做才變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.43,0:08:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼當時動得那麼順暢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是能搞清楚{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.06,0:08:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再說你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是在讀那個說明書似的玩意罷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.19,0:08:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是技師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真沒禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有我就沒有銀色殲滅者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼動不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.30,0:08:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是劃時代的新系統嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在那時{\rsymbol}…{\r}是第一次參戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只顧拼命根本什麼都不記得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:08:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但下一次{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我到底哪裡不對 你倒是看清點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由於進行著金屬精煉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這礦山除採掘隧道之外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有很大的煙道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能走這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,席加 你先去探探
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快能清理完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.42,0:09:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 敵人也不簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 真正棘手的是來回逃竄的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.76,0:09:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,棘手?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不該很好對付的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白逃跑意義的人 必定存於敗退之軍中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.71,0:09:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要抹殺這些未來的強敵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:09:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,記住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄礦山嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這邊狀況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garm-1 已向那邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,軍糧 終於咽得下去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狀態如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還可以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很用功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這點大家都認可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希爾菲雖然還很苛刻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但銀色殲滅者只有你能駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.47,0:10:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快記起來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.65,0:10:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快記起來 吉米
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你絕對學過的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.73,0:11:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.48,0:11:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有這樣的洞窟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是洞窟 是煙道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煙道(遠藤)先生?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.34,0:11:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是排煙的通路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉上嘴快走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 新來的 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.46,0:12:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是去操縱{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼做來著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 笨死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.67,0:12:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對{\rsymbol}…{\r}對不起 我自言自語
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.36,0:12:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然在這
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.89,0:12:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把載具扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-2 如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不到人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我翻過山去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別大意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.96,0:12:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 請繼續監視
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左文字隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了 共三部
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.17,0:13:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.17,0:13:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谷田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.88,0:13:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗機掉隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這要爬山還有點難
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-2 回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.36,0:13:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到疑似逃跑路徑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進上等兵 收到請回話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人順煙道追來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 這怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.46,0:14:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就結果而言 你現在是殿后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫<殿后> 軍校裡學過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂<殿后>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是阻止敵人追擊 掩護友軍撤離
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令 擋住他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.50,0:14:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重複一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把敵人擋在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尾久井上等兵帶吉米小姐儘快與大部隊匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.77,0:14:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀色殲滅者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有那個叫時宗的怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為掩護你們與敵人交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很危險 你們儘快離開那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扔下不管?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前腳剛接收 後腳就要拋棄銀色殲滅者?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.98,0:14:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過分 太自作主張了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:14:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,銀色殲滅者只有進上等兵才能駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.47,0:15:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是關乎部隊存亡的判斷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還以為你是個好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是說得什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把一個新兵留下自己逃跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.73,0:15:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,服從命令是士兵的天職
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平民給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但再怎麼說這命令也太沒天理了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.22,0:15:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你當初不也無視命令救了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在這才是最佳選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尾久井 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.82,0:15:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.80,0:17:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我說得不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要想著怎麼操縱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想像一下 你現在想做什麼 怎樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.35,0:17:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不為獲勝 也不為被人認同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是為了活下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行了 老實跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別隨便瞎跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請放下我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟銀色殲滅者{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令 要我帶你安全歸隊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.97,0:18:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.33,0:18:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來不對啊{\rsymbol}…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.48,0:18:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.31,0:18:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是隊長說的新型機?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟訓練時學的技法不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接拳打腳踢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方只有一部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夾擊他 掩護我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不戰鬥就會被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不能死在這
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.25,0:19:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧 G-3
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還能動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是什麼玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要輸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,時宗 過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:19:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈～身手不減當年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迷死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣 帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下身後追兵暫時能拖一陣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但前面不知道有多少敵人等著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鈴城
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個小姑娘 你怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.07,0:21:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您指吉米小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.71,0:21:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他倆搭檔不錯啊 她和時宗君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.29,0:21:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈茲福特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.56,0:21:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫吉米就行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那{\rsymbol}…{\r}吉米
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.80,0:21:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.32,0:21:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我是50對50
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.39,0:21:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個 打算如何處理
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.91,0:21:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.15,0:21:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
