Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.98,0:01:39.60,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}胸中的意志將一飛沖天
Dialogue: 1,0:01:50.87,0:01:55.68,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}Fake… 那火光是戰友嗎{\fnSource Han Sans Medium}?
